import React from 'react'
import Card from '../UI/Card/Card'
import Input from './Input'

const Register = () => {
  return (
   <Card>
    <form>
      <Input 
        label='Password'
        type='password' 
        id='password'
        placeholder='enter password'/>
    </form>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default Register
